### Get All Students (no auth)
GET {{base}}/students

### Get current student (Auth required) – returns profile for the authenticated user
GET {{base}}/students/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Get single student by ID (no auth)
GET {{base}}/students/N1373616

### Get pending ratings for a student (no auth)
GET {{base}}/students/N1373616/pending-ratings

### --- EVENTS ---
### Note: POST /events, register, cancel-registration, PUT, DELETE, my-events, my-registrations require Authorization: Bearer <firebase-id-token>. Publisher ID = publisher's NTU ID (set from token on create). Event ID is auto-generated (1, 2, 3, ...); do not send eventId in POST body.

### Create event 1 – React Workshop (Auth required; eventId auto-generated, publisherId set from token)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "publisherId": "N1373616",
  "title": "React Workshop",
  "type": "Workshop",
  "date": "2026-03-15",
  "time": "14:00",
  "duration": 180,
  "location": "NG1 4FQ",
  "venue": "Computer Lab A, City Campus",
  "cost": 0.0,
  "maxParticipants": 30,
  "description": "Join us for an intensive React workshop covering hooks, state and component design."
}

### Create event 2 – Java Study Group (assigned id 2)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "publisherId": "N2001001",
  "title": "Java Study Group",
  "type": "Workshop",
  "date": "2026-03-18",
  "time": "10:00",
  "duration": 120,
  "location": "NG11 8NS",
  "venue": "Main Hall, Clifton Campus",
  "cost": 0.0,
  "maxParticipants": 25,
  "description": "Weekly study group for Java and Spring. Bring your laptop and questions."
}

### Create event 3 – Career Fair (assigned id 3)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "publisherId": "N2001002",
  "title": "Career Fair",
  "type": "Career",
  "date": "2026-03-22",
  "time": "09:00",
  "duration": 360,
  "location": "NG1 4BU",
  "venue": "Newton Building, City Campus",
  "cost": 0.0,
  "maxParticipants": 200,
  "description": "Employers from tech, finance and engineering. CV advice and networking."
}

### Create event 4 – Sports Day (assigned id 4)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "publisherId": "N2001003",
  "title": "Sports Day",
  "type": "Sports",
  "date": "2026-03-25",
  "time": "11:00",
  "duration": 240,
  "location": "NG11 8NS",
  "venue": "Sports Centre, Clifton Campus",
