}

### Create event 5 – Hackathon (assigned id 5)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "publisherId": "N2001004",
  "title": "24h Hackathon",
  "type": "Workshop",
  "date": "2026-04-01",
  "time": "12:00",
  "duration": 1440,
  "location": "NG1 4FQ",
  "venue": "Boots Library, City Campus",
  "cost": 0.0,
  "maxParticipants": 50,
  "description": "Build a project in 24 hours. Prizes for best app, best design and best pitch."
}

### Get All Events (no auth)
GET {{base}}/events

### Get events with optional filters (no auth)
GET {{base}}/events?type=Workshop

###
GET {{base}}/events?location=NG1

###
GET {{base}}/events?type=Career&location=NG1

### --- MY EVENTS (Auth required) – new endpoints ---

### Get events published by the current user (publisherId = student linked to token)
GET {{base}}/events/my-events
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Get events the current user is registered for (attendees contains studentId from token)
GET {{base}}/events/my-registrations
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### --- REGISTER / CANCEL REGISTRATION (Auth required) ---
### Register: current user (from token) is added to event attendees. Use numeric event id (1, 2, 3, ...).

### Register for event 1 (send as logged-in student, e.g. N1373616)
POST {{base}}/events/1/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Register for event 2
POST {{base}}/events/2/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Register for event 3
POST {{base}}/events/3/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Register for event 4
POST {{base}}/events/4/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Register for event 5
POST {{base}}/events/5/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Cancel registration – remove current user from event attendees (Auth required)
POST {{base}}/events/1/cancel-registration
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### --- UPDATE / DELETE EVENT (Auth required; only publisher can update/delete) ---

### Update event 1 (body: full event; attendees/ratings preserved server-side)
PUT {{base}}/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

{
  "eventId": "1",
  "publisherId": "N1373616",
  "title": "React Workshop (Updated)",
  "type": "Workshop",
  "date": "2026-03-15",
  "time": "15:00",
  "duration": 180,
  "location": "NG1 4FQ",
  "venue": "Computer Lab A, City Campus",
  "cost": 0.0,
  "maxParticipants": 35,
  "description": "Updated: Join us for an intensive React workshop covering hooks, state and component design."
}

### Delete event (only publisher; use an event id you published)
DELETE {{base}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### Get single event (no auth) – check attendees count after register/cancel
GET {{base}}/events/1

### --- FINISHED EVENTS (past date – for rating tests) ---
### Create these after events 1–5; they get auto-assigned ids 6, 7, 8. Use those ids in the paths below.

### Past React Refresher (assigned id 6)
POST {{base}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

