### Register for finished events (Auth required – use token for N1373616, N2001001, etc. in turn). Use ids 6, 7, 8.
POST {{base}}/events/6/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

POST {{base}}/events/7/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

POST {{base}}/events/8/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth}}

### --- POST-EVENT RATINGS (use studentId in body) ---

### Get event rating before any ratings (event 6: 0 average, 0 count)
GET {{base}}/events/6/rating

### Pending events to rate for a student
GET {{base}}/students/N1373616/pending-ratings

### Submit ratings for event 6
POST {{base}}/events/6/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N1373616",
  "rating": 4
}

POST {{base}}/events/6/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001001",
  "rating": 5
}

POST {{base}}/events/6/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001002",
  "rating": 3
}

### Get event 6 rating after 3 ratings (average 4.0, count 3)
GET {{base}}/events/6/rating

### Submit ratings for event 7
POST {{base}}/events/7/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001001",
  "rating": 5
}

POST {{base}}/events/7/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001003",
  "rating": 4
}

POST {{base}}/events/7/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "T2001001",
  "rating": 4
}

GET {{base}}/events/7/rating

### Submit ratings for event 8
POST {{base}}/events/8/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001002",
  "rating": 5
}

POST {{base}}/events/8/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001004",
  "rating": 4
}

POST {{base}}/events/8/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N1373616",
  "rating": 5
}

GET {{base}}/events/8/rating

### Pending ratings after rating (should be empty when all rated)
GET {{base}}/students/N1373616/pending-ratings

### Change rating (last write wins) – same student resubmits for event 6
POST {{base}}/events/6/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N1373616",
  "rating": 2
}

### Rate when not attendee – N2001005 did not register for event 6 (should return 400 Bad Request)
POST {{base}}/events/6/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001005",
  "rating": 4
}

### Rate upcoming event 1 (not ended – should return 400 Bad Request)
POST {{base}}/events/1/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N1373616",
  "rating": 4
}

### Invalid rating value (must be 1–5, should return 400)
POST {{base}}/events/7/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "N2001001",
  "rating": 6
}

### Upcoming events – get rating (no ratings yet)
GET {{base}}/events/1/rating

### Get rating (event 2)
GET {{base}}/events/2/rating

### --- EXTERNAL APIs ---

### Geocode UK postcode
GET {{base}}/external/geocode?postcode=NG14FQ

### Weather by postcode (Open-Meteo)
GET {{base}}/external/weather?postcode=NG14FQ

### Map embed URL by postcode (Google Maps Embed API key required)
GET {{base}}/external/map-embed-url?postcode=NG14FQ

### Map embed URL by place name
GET {{base}}/external/map-embed-url?place=Nottingham

### Reverse geocode (lat/long to postcode/display name)
GET {{base}}/external/reverse-geocode?latitude=52.9548&longitude=-1.1581

### Nearby public events (Skiddle; lat, long, radius in miles)
GET {{base}}/external/nearby-events?latitude=52.9548&longitude=-1.1581&radius=20